description:
Danny welcomes the wonderful Candice King (Vampire Diaries actress and host of the Directionally Challenged podcast) to break down this week's Vanderpump Rules. This week the girls returned from Solvang, Lala begins drinking again, Kristin and Carter hash it out, and Kristina Kelly/Kathy returns to our TVs.


Candice King/Vanderpump Recap: 3:26ish
